Blogs Endpoints

Method	Endpoint	Payload	Description
POST	/api/blogs	{ "title": "Blog Title", "content": "Content here", "author": "John" }	Create a new blog
GET	/api/blogs	None	Get all blogs
GET	/api/blogs/:id	None	Get a single blog
PUT	/api/blogs/:id	{ "title": "Updated Title" }	Update a blog
DELETE	/api/blogs/:id	None	Delete a blog


Newsletter Endpoints

Method	Endpoint	Payload	Description
POST	/api/newsletters/subscribe	{ "email": "user@example.com" }	Subscribe to the newsletter
GET	/api/newsletters	None	Get all subscriptions
GET	/api/newsletters/:id	None	Get a single subscription
PUT	/api/newsletters/:id	{ "email": "new@example.com" }	Update a subscription
DELETE	/api/newsletters/:id	None	Delete a subscription